tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE protein_interactions (
 protein_id INT,
 interaction_partner_id INT,
 interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
 interaction_score FLOAT,
 interaction_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ProteinInteraction (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protein_a_id INT,
    protein_b_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_strength FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Protein (
    protein_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protein_name VARCHAR(100),
    gene_symbol VARCHAR(50),
    protein_type VARCHAR(50),
    organism VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE InteractionRegion (
    region_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_id INT,
    region_name VARCHAR(100),
    region_start INT,
    region_end INT
);
